! TMDS Timing-Plane Invariants

The HDMI/TMDS timing layer treated as a deterministic clock-law plane for
state packets and witness routing.

!! Why It Matters

This splits [[HDMI Compute Fabric]] into a concrete timing primitive: the
transport is not just pixels, it is ordered symbols with cadence, blanking,
and synchronization structure.

